($d$Collection / Dining Table Set$d$, $d$Emry Rectangular Statuario Ceramic 6 Seater Dining Table With 6  Clarke Dining Chairs (Finish : Danish Walnut, Chair Colour : Tan Leatherette) - Urban Ladder$d$, $d$ByUrban Ladder$d$, $d$: Tan Leatherette)$d$, 12, NULL, $d$90$d$, $d$1$d$, $d$76$d$, $d$47.05 kg$d$, $d$Designed for homes that celebrate everyday elegance, the Emry-Clarke dining set blends sculptural form with natural warmth.Â  The Emry table anchors the space with sophistication, its smooth ceramic top, framed by a floating edge, rests gracefully on a solid mango wood base. Elegant veining traces across the surface, catching light and conversation alike.  Surrounding it, the Clarke chairs bring a charm to the ensemble. Their gently contoured backrests and cushioned seats invite long, unhurried meals, while the solid wood frame lends timeless strength and texture. Subtle curves and tapered legs give the silhouette a poised lightness.  Together, they create a dining experience defined by harmony, of materials, craftsmanship, and the simple pleasure of gathering around good design.  Available in 4 and 6 seater options.$d$, NULL, $d$Solid Wood$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 70496.0, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/wuGaMfcPV-0.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/l4MPkjqfiV-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/AV2vdq8J6o-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/aWBoRciZc0-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/DMq6s6wGRG-5.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/BpPYfjq9Yy-6.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/p