($d$Collection / Dining Table Set$d$, $d$Dune Solid Oak Wood Dining Table With 6 Dune Solid Wood Dining Chairs (Finish : Gradient Oak, Chair Colour : Deep Olive Velvet) - Urban Ladder$d$, $d$ByUrban Ladder$d$, $d$: Deep Olive Velvet)$d$, 12, NULL, $d$90$d$, $d$1$d$, $d$72$d$, $d$86.00 kg$d$, $d$Inspired by the natural poetry of desert landscapes, the Dune dining set brings together fluid form and organic materiality. The Dune dining table captures the soft gradation of dusk across its rounded oak wood top, where natural texture and gentle curves create a sense of calm movement. Palm treeÃâinspired legs add sculptural character, grounding the design while keeping it light and expressive. Paired with the Dune dining chairs, the setting feels cohesive and inviting. The chairscurved silhouette and plush upholstery introduce softness, while the warmth of wood adds depth and tactility. Together, the Dune table and chairs create a dining space that feels ethereal, welcoming, and made to linger around. Available in a 6-seater option.$d$, NULL, $d$Solid Wood$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 118993.0, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/XnLdpxMdM-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/tq1hM1W3r-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/u46HgMcO4-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/sP6XggIph0-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/bsiLh7jO3H-5.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/OUlVjAuF16-6.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/KGf62HVvYy-7.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patien