($d$Collection / Dining Chairs$d$, $d$Atlas Solid Wood Dining Chairs Set Of 2 in Honey Finish with Baltic Blue Colour$d$, $d$ByUrban Ladder$d$, $d$Chair Finish : Honey Qty : 1$d$, 36, NULL, $d$49$d$, $d$45$d$, $d$89$d$, $d$21.35 kg$d$, $d$Gather, linger, and savour every moment—because the Atlas Dining Chairs are designed for more than just meals. With their plush upholstered seating, they invite you to sit back and stay awhile, while their clean lines and contemporary design add effortless elegance to any space. Crafted from solid Mango wood and finished in a rich, warm tone, Atlas blends seamlessly into a variety of settings, from modern dining rooms to cozy breakfast nooks. A perfect balance of comfort and style, Atlas makes every moment feel special. - Available in Honey and Danish Walnut finish options. - Made from solid Mango wood. - Pair with Atlas Dining Table for a seamless look.$d$, NULL, $d$Solid Wood$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9999.0, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/RkA-tfc7oIg-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/ra9XT-7HepV-2.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/O2E8uklJVxj-3.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/wz-2Wu6QCR6-4.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/JFStoe_iq-Atlas-Dining-Chairs-Set-of-2-Finish-Danish-walnut-Colour-Avocado-Green.png | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/RkA-tfc7oIg-1.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/zwBt3bFtxzm-02.png | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/ra9XT-7HepV-2.jpg | http