($d$Collection / Dining Chairs$d$, $d$Beck Swivel Metal Dining Chair Set Of 2 In Wine Fabric$d$, $d$ByUrban Ladder$d$, $d$Olive Leatherette Taupe Leatherette Wine$d$, 12, NULL, $d$66$d$, $d$61$d$, $d$91$d$, $d$19.50 kg$d$, $d$Settle into effortless style with the Beck dining chair. Its lounge-inspired silhouette embraces you with contoured creases on the backrest and seat, offering a tailored yet relaxed appeal. The high back and gently angled arms provide ergonomic support, inviting longer meals or quiet moments of reflection. A sleek swivel base lends a modern edge, letting you turn or rise with effortless ease. Perfect for chic dining spaces or home offices, Beck turns every moment into a lasting impression. - High-back design for effortless comfort. - Premium 330GSM fabric in Wine fabric and premium leatherette in Taupe and Olive leatherette. - Sleek metal legs in black finish.$d$, NULL, $d$Metal$d$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 24999.0, $d$https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/5fP-oCz4n--LP.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/nq_68k2gC-b.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/v9yj9gHkN_-a.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/yIfmocLYyT-c.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/-2w19hQAN-e.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/100x0/DuZSF7wPRh-f.png | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/original/5fP-oCz4n--LP.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/free/150x0/q-AdoyL4--b.jpg | https://cdn.swadeshonline.com/v2/patient-paper-41f385/swad-p/wrkr/products/pictures/item/fre